{"tid":1696926,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【忽發奇想】結合換美金同黃色經濟圈兩大戰線","createTime":"2019-11-06T13:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T00:47:19.000Z","uid":180415,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6878267c84cfc6911992225b01c2c448b7c2f1","tid":1696926,"uid":180415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:29:55.000Z","msg":"首先唔清楚香港用美金交易係咪合法，google過好似冇咩點講，求專業人士意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩突然諗到如果所有黃店慢慢逐步開始收美金，再之後變成完全淨收美金，會唔會對變相鼓勵到啲懶換美金嘅人，或者覺得換左美金會少左錢可以日常用嘅人換多啲美金。咁樣做長遠黎講仲可以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">繼續衝擊香港美金嘅儲備，甚至令港紙愈來愈少人用</span></strong></strong></span></span>，唔知到時人仔會唔會借唔到港紙黎換美金呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過缺點係有機會令啲人因為麻煩而減少幫襯黃店，所以都係要靠大家嘅堅持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c4eeee1298298d67f8d94b03656617f1267700","tid":1696926,"uid":180415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"自推x1"},{"pid":"110099695a4b6bab3cdc4aea51aa46b95ad88a2c","tid":1696926,"uid":180415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:31:11.000Z","msg":"自推x2"},{"pid":"9b419886356c3277f70f7523e6dbb37ef862e110","tid":1696926,"uid":180415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:32:02.000Z","msg":"自推x3"},{"pid":"d6bcdd767b55d15013cfe629ddb0be6c0ac61b91","tid":1696926,"uid":180415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"自推x4"},{"pid":"b27d9c93d134f8ee280b19c0dbe15f158a704873","tid":1696926,"uid":180415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"自推x5"},{"pid":"0eb5d5dd6a66b2c6e1ded280de0bda806d9e5173","tid":1696926,"uid":180415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"自推x6"},{